From 064635c67f11c2657a8f3f33761b303c6abe4839 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: KITOHSY <hongsun900912@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 10:06:55 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] T13: register moonlight:// URL scheme in Linux .desktop
 file
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

SmartClassroom T13 — adds MimeType=x-scheme-handler/moonlight; and an
%u placeholder on the Exec line so that xdg-open and browsers route
moonlight://connect?... URLs (issued by the SmartClassroom Broker
frontend) to this binary. main.cpp's URL handler then expands the URL
into the `connect` CLI subcommand and dispatches into ComputerManager.

Distro packages (apt/rpm) and Flatpak builds pick the new MimeType up
when update-desktop-database runs during package install. AppImage
users need a one-time `xdg-mime default com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop
x-scheme-handler/moonlight` because AppImages do not run the desktop-
database hook; that step is documented in client-patches/moonlight-qt/
BUILD.md.
---
 app/deploy/linux/com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop | 7 ++++++-
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/app/deploy/linux/com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop b/app/deploy/linux/com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop
index a393b247..9d4e2646 100644
--- a/app/deploy/linux/com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop
+++ b/app/deploy/linux/com.moonlight_stream.Moonlight.desktop
@@ -1,9 +1,14 @@
 [Desktop Entry]
 Name=Moonlight
 Comment=Stream games and other applications from another PC running Sunshine or GeForce Experience
-Exec=moonlight
+Exec=moonlight %u
 Icon=moonlight
 Terminal=false
 Type=Application
 Categories=Qt;Game;
 Keywords=nvidia;gamestream;stream;sunshine;remote play;
+# SmartClassroom T13 — claim the moonlight:// URL scheme so xdg-open / browsers
+# route moonlight://connect?... URLs (from the SmartClassroom Broker frontend)
+# to this binary. `%u` carries the URL as argv[1]; main.cpp expands it into
+# the `connect` CLI subcommand and dispatches to ComputerManager.
+MimeType=x-scheme-handler/moonlight;
